Class Basic

java.lang.Object
data.Member
data.Basic
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Member>
public class Basic extends Member
Represents a Basic membership in the gym system. Extends the Member class to include attributes and behaviors specific to Basic memberships, such as tracking the number of classes attended and calculating the bill based on attendance.
Author:
Soham Patel
